{"tid":542603,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(睇到都痛)一人一個目前為止覺得最痛既經歷","createTime":"2018-01-27T15:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T17:34:46.000Z","uid":4689,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"0802bf457d1ee501538777a106c4bb2134b71cbd","tid":542603,"uid":4689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"之前生過疱疹性烟喉炎，果個星期成個口爛哂，唔好話飲水食野 連大開個口都唔得，每日痛到醒 野又食唔到，個種痛大約等餘你個口生滿飛滋 每朝/晚刷牙好似去左地獄走左轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最慘係無得食藥好 只可以等佢慢慢好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f61a744e31adf1da8c18182388f16000174dc4","tid":542603,"uid":78785,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"吹水大會開始"},{"pid":"dad4ab6daa096171bac3ff20f0d5ad5b40e87433","tid":542603,"uid":49853,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"拉褲鍊夾到包皮"},{"pid":"6a9ad506006f198b1e685ab09960dee53bffa377","tid":542603,"uid":13695,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"腳指尾撞枱腳"},{"pid":"ca62594364635752731eedd0345f49dc4ac2f60a","tid":542603,"uid":67976,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"把生果刀喺枱面然後跌左落黎斬左半隻腳趾公<br />\n<br />\n不過而家無野"},{"pid":"b01ab62772cb83b6636dc598533010e4303ff76d","tid":542603,"uid":4689,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dad4ab6daa096171bac3ff20f0d5ad5b40e87433","tid":542603,"uid":49853,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"拉褲鍊夾到包皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"淨係試過夾鳩毛 都痛到標眼水"},{"pid":"d927d56a89b3ea1ecadb368fbb6c02034ee90602","tid":542603,"uid":4689,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca62594364635752731eedd0345f49dc4ac2f60a","tid":542603,"uid":67976,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"repl